            <strong><li>Running the server</li></strong>
            <li>* Serve an ember app in development.</li>
            <strong><li>Basic testing</li></strong>
            <li>* Generate an acceptance test and run the <a href="https://guides.emberjs.com/v2.3.0/testing/">test suite</a>.</li>
