            <li>* Introduce how Ember deals with asynchronous behavior.</li>
            <strong><li>Routes</li></strong>
            <li>* Learn what gives structure to an Ember application.</li>
            <strong><li>Components</li></strong>
            <li>* Share reusable templates and behavior.</li>
            <strong><li>Actions</li></strong>
            <li>* Trigger changes based on user input.</li>
            <strong><li>Services</li></strong>
            <li>* Move persistent state out of short lived components.</li>
            <strong><li>Add-ons</li></strong>
            <li>* Utilize community driven and proven solutions.</li>
            <strong><li>Helpers</li></strong>
            <li>* Extract small pieces of reusable template code.</li>
          </ul>
        </p>
