          <ul>
            <strong><li>Advanced testing</li></strong>
            <li>* <a href="https://guides.emberjs.com/v2.3.0/testing/acceptance/">Acceptance tests</a></li>
            <li>* <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/ember-cli-page-object">Page objects</a></li>
            <li>* <a href="https://guides.emberjs.com/v2.3.0/testing/testing-components/">Integration tests</a> (components)</li>
            <li>* <a href="https://guides.emberjs.com/v2.3.0/testing/unit-testing-basics/">Unit tests</a> (helpers, routes, services)</li>
            <strong><li>Authentication using Torii and Ember-Simple-Auth</li></strong>
            <li>* Account creation</li>
            <li>* Account update</li>
            <li>* OAuth sign in</li>
            <strong><li>APIs and Ember-CLI-Mirage</li></strong>
            <li>* <a href="http://emberjs.com/api/data/classes/DS.JSONAPIAdapter.html">JSON API</a></li>
            <li>* <a href="http://www.ember-cli-mirage.com/">Mocking an API</a></li>
            <li>* Live JSON API</li>
