            <li>* <a href="https://guides.emberjs.com/v2.3.0/models/">Creating a model</a></li>
            <li>* <a href="https://guides.emberjs.com/v2.3.0/models/creating-updating-and-deleting-records/">Persisting a model</a></li>
            <strong><li>Deployment</li></strong>
            <li>* Deploy your Ember apps easily and confidently with <a href="http://ember-cli.com/ember-cli-deploy/">ember-cli-deploy</a>.</li>
            <strong><li>Sockets</li></strong>
            <li>* Learn how to integrate real-time data into Ember Data with sockets.</li>
          </ul>
